data.description: A Beautiful Main Floor Owner Suite Home in the Maintained Community of Windance, this Exceptional home features a Den on the 1st flr, Tiled Owner Bath Ste, Lrg Tiled Walk-in Shower, Kitchen appointed w Quartz Counters & Stainless appl, 9' ceilings & Soaring Cathedral ceilings in Great rm, French Doors at Den, Loft & 4th possible bdrm/Bonus Room, gas Fireplace. Spacious  NEW Deck 2023 overlooking the Golf Course on the 15 hole. NEW Roof 2023. 200 SqFt storage under house w concrete slab, high ceilings & lights. All this Plus a short walk to Northshore Golf Course. Front Yard Maintenance, Rear Yard Mowing only & Exterior Paint of homes Maintained thru HOD's. THROW AWAY PAINT BRUSHES & MOWER IT IS TIME TO RELAX & ENJOY LIFE AT WINDANCE.
